"Simulate random date fetch delays" = "Simulasi kelewatan rawak semasa mendapatkan tarikh";
"Debug" = "Nyahpepijat";
"When enabled, each date fetch is delayed by a random duration between 0 and twice the timeout. If the random delay exceeds the timeout, the fetch is aborted as if a timeout occurred." = "Apabila didayakan, setiap pengambilan tarikh dilewatkan selama tempoh rawak antara 0 dan dua kali tamat masa. Jika kelewatan rawak melebihi tamat masa, pengambilan dibatalkan seperti tamat masa sebenar.";
